It is easy and as a bonus you know that your car is not blocking the city space.

- Try online calculator and you will know exactly how much you will pay: https://www.autonapul.cz/kalkulacka/

- You pay for kilometres driven and time booked, combined.
- You always have the car that you need. Small for the city, big for your vacation.
- Cars are booked online with your computer or smartphone.
- Available 24/7
- Book a car for just a few hours, half day business trips, weekends with your family or for the whole vacation
- Very good for companies and freelancers
- No worries about servicing the car, insurance or the hassle of buying a car. Everything will be sorted for you.

- There is no better option for customers who drive less than 10.000km per year.
- Car sharing saves not only your purse but the environment and city space, too.
- Car sharing fits great with your daily commute with public transportation or by bicycle. It is best combined with trains and buses for longer trips.

Where can I find Autonapul?
Our cars are in: Brno, Praha, Olomouc, Ostrava, Liberec, Plzeň, Hradec Králové, Pardubice, České Budějovice

How do you join in?

Register at www.autonapul.cz/chci-se-pridat

Allow a working day after your payment to activate your account. And you can go for your trip.

Autonapul creates space for people. Together. One shared car replaces up to ten privately owned cars in the city.
